Introduction

DSSHOP所有API接口文档

本文档旨在提供您使用我们的API所需的所有信息。

当你滚动屏幕时，你会在右边的黑暗区域看到使用不同编程语言的API的代码示例(或作为移动内容的一部分)。 你可以通过右上角的选项卡切换语言(或者在移动设备上从左上角的导航菜单)。

Base URL

http://dsshop.test

Authenticating requests

This API is not authenticated.

[CLIENT]User(用户)

Class UserController

UserCancel 注销账号

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/app/cancel" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/app/cancel"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
Received response:
Request failed with error:

Request      

POST api/v1/app/cancel

UserEdit 保存用户信息

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/app/user?portrait=ut&nickname=exercitationem" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/app/user"
);

const params = {
    "portrait": "ut",
    "nickname": "exercitationem",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
Received response:
Request failed with error:

Request      

POST api/v1/app/user

Query Parameters

portrait  string optional  

头像

nickname  string optional  

昵称

UserDetail 用户信息

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/app/user" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/app/user"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

[CLIENT]Goods(商品)

Class GoodController

GoodCategory 商品分类

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/app/goodCategory?tree=&is_recommend=19&limit=2&sort=aut&page=tempore" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/app/goodCategory"
);

const params = {
    "tree": "0",
    "is_recommend": "19",
    "limit": "2",
    "sort": "aut",
    "page": "tempore",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

Example response (401):

Request      

GET api/v1/app/goodCategory

Query Parameters

tree  boolean optional  

返回格式是否为树状结构

is_recommend  integer optional  

是否首页展示

limit  integer optional  

每页显示条数

sort  string optional  

排序

page  string optional  

页码

GoodDetail 商品详情

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/app/good/laboriosam?id=14" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/admin?name=reprehenderit&email=similique&cellphone=8&portrait=cum&password=dignissimos" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/admin"
);

const params = {
    "name": "reprehenderit",
    "email": "similique",
    "cellphone": "8",
    "portrait": "cum",
    "password": "dignissimos",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

    --header "Accept: application/json"

    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/indent"

DhlCreate 创建快递公司

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/dhl?name=voluptatem&abbreviation=molestiae&state=architecto&sort=deleniti" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/dhl"
);

const params = {
    "name": "voluptatem",
    "abbreviation": "molestiae",
    "state": "architecto",
    "sort": "deleniti",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

PlugInUninstall 插件卸载

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/plugin/uninstall/officiis?name=necessitatibus" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/plugin/uninstall/officiis"
);

const params = {
    "name": "necessitatibus",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
